{"tid":2202349,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"老毛拜墓 - 顏純鈎","createTime":"2020-09-14T13:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T13:48:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18125774e61fb4b927b63fe194e93dbd337b9615","tid":2202349,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200914/SCGV2V7W65BFNENVKB5Z4PAO5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200914%2FSCGV2V7W65BFNENVKB5Z4PAO5Q%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacbVsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=c0993a63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200914%2FSCGV2V7W65BFNENVKB5Z4PAO5Q%2F&h=266cb3d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200914/SCGV2V7W65BFNENVKB5Z4PAO5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n老毛拜墓 - 顏純鈎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/n1exKzIwO58GcynHmZZz6Xc4aZY=/5624x3892/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BQWZXYVRGNH23FWCANRJ7OXH7Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fn1exKzIwO58GcynHmZZz6Xc4aZY%3D%2F5624x3892%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBQWZXYVRGNH23FWCANRJ7OXH7Y.jpg&h=9e4bed29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有視頻，拍到一個農村野地，一個貌似毛澤東的人，在大動作作跪拜之禮。原來是有村民父母親在文革中被害死，村民便花錢僱一個毛澤東替身，到父母墳前叩頭謝罪，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n冤有頭債有主，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國人不是沒有創意的，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東集古今中外諸惡之大成。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n從反右到三年大饑荒，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n所有的獨裁者身後，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動以來，警察打死打傷香港年輕人不可勝數，誰下的命令，誰做的策劃，誰手上染血，一筆筆血債，都會記在香港史冊上，留在香港人心中。日後會不會有人追隨毛澤東，被人花錢僱替身來行跪拜之禮，那就各自去衡量了。<br />\n<br />\n陸遊詩有句「身後是非誰管得，滿村聽說蔡中郎。」人死萬事空，但生前身後名各有因果，身後是非絕不是沒有人「管得」，而是千古之下人人管得。今日沒有人僱胡耀邦替身去拜自己的父母，證明政治人物之功過，人民自有定論。<br />\n<br />\n世道日壞，。。。。"},{"pid":"a78f573f78690c2ffa55dfbec81722ac59366fc0","tid":2202349,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"老毛拜墓有冇片？未睇過"}]}